Just a work in progress, still much work to do.

The following areas are ready for testing:                   
1. Basement (Bottom Floor)                             
2. Lab Floor (2nd to Bottom Floor)                    

KEY NOTE: Find the generator room and press "E" to activate the generators which turn on the facility lights!

KEY NOTE: Pressing "E" on any of the vents will open them. Repeat the process to close them.
